<L>__{exterior depot plaszow day}
<A>__{the sun is higher, the cattle cars hotter. prisoners' arms stretch out between the slats offering diamonds in exchange for a sip of water.}
<L>__{exterior plaszow later day}
<A>__{the needle of the phonograph is set down on another record, a children's song, "mammi, kauf mir ein pferdchen" (mommy, buy me a pony). children are yanked from the arms of their parents. wailing protests quickly escalate to brawls with the guards. revolvers and rifles aim at the sun and fire. music, shots, wails.}
